\u00f2 a sussistere come Automobile Monteverdi. Nel 1990 M. fu proprietario, per dieci corse, della scuderia Onyx di formula uno."]], "wiki_links": [{"item": "http://www.wikidata.org/entity/Q117190", "itemLabel": "Peter Monteverdi", "dhsid": "045537", "namefr": "Peter Monteverdi", "articlefr": "https://fr.wikipedia.org/wiki/Peter_Monteverdi", "namede": "Peter Monteverdi", "articlede": "https://de.wikipedia.org/wiki/Peter_Monteverdi", "nameit": "Peter Monteverdi", "articleit": "https://it.wikipedia.org/wiki/Peter_Monteverdi", "nameen": "Peter Monteverdi", "articleen": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Peter_Monteverdi", "instanceof": "http://www.wikidata.org/entity/Q5", "instanceofLabel": "\u00eatre humain", "gndid": "134127986"}], "wikidata_url": "http://www.wikidata.org/entity/Q117190", "wikipedia_page_title": "Peter Monteverdi", "added_wikidata_wikipedia_to_text_links": true, "_initial": "M", "url": "https://hls-dhs-dss.ch/it/articles/045537/2008-11-27"}